metadata.name: Piece of Penguins
metadata.description:
Piece of Wild is my personal project in which I took animal painting one step further.

When I first saw this picture I was amazed at how the penguins held hands, in the freezing cold of Antarctica, in that moment I realized I had found my next muse!

I wish those who hold this piece peace, tranquility, health and a good relationship.
